HEADWORD: Bowyer
<hw>Bow"yer</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From <er>Bow</er>,
like <ets>lawyer</ets> from <ets>law</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
